{"tid":1300220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］TG 18區舉報暴徒大行動","createTime":"2019-07-09T09:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T10:07:09.000Z","uid":45299,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd36f7a954deb8d56156a935008941246d03978","tid":1300220,"uid":45299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"一齊入去幫手搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記得注意安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*我哋班苦主真係好慘呀 😭😭😭*<br />\n<br />\n好鍾意玩遍地開花 ⁉ 嗱~依家成全你😡 <br />\n<br />\n遍地開花🌸18區舉報暴徒大行動💪<br />\n<br />\n暴徒個個禮拜區區搞事，蝦阿婆阿伯、打女人，假借自由之名任意破壞、打人、立法會都拆咗，民怨四起， 一班為生活嘅苦主唯有發起群組，請大家自己揾返所屬自己所居住嘅災區，喺安全情況下拍攝暴徒真面目及惡行。<br />\n<br />\n(記得遇險時記得除下暴徒口罩，佢哋會好似隻鬼👻咁見光死🙈)<br />\n<br />\n之後上載、我們會每星期sent 交去警局、各國領事館、入境處 😎 唔止遍到開花，我哋幫暴徙全球開化 🤣<br />\n<br />\n*各位唔見咗仔女嘅街坊可以試吓入返自己區内搵下，可能有機會揾返佢哋😢*<br />\n<br />\n*中 西 區*: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Mu4blhE0lxHxjZsUUPXo_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMu4blhE0lxHxjZsUUPXo_A&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7EoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=e7b039a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Mu4blhE0lxHxjZsUUPXo_A</a><br />\n<br />\n*灣 仔 區*: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Mu4blhd3P_tIyLxFtI_6RQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMu4blhd3P_tIyLxFtI_6RQ&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7EoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=d0371297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Mu4blhd3P_tIyLxFtI_6RQ</a><br />\n<br />\n*東 區* :<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Mu4blhIKxl2cfVkroDOfTQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMu4blhIKxl2cfVk